{"tid":938864,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我有潔癖 但我大佬為人極度污糟 點做好?","createTime":"2018-12-12T15:56:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T01:19:32.000Z","uid":199590,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"16616b4a3460a324cabfdd592b74070c6f648182","tid":938864,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T15:56:46.000Z","msg":"事先聲明 今次真係認真post嚟 唔係假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平時有啲咩屋企清潔都係我做 我一定會做到盡量一塵不染 每日都會用酒精消毒抹布抹下啲洗手盆 門柄嗰啲 做啲基本清潔嗰類嘢 <br />\n<br />\n但佢平時喺咕𠱸上面食嘢R面皮 整到成個咕𠱸都係面皮同食物碎 痾尿痾到周地都係 成隻狗痾尿噉 嗰啲我都好少屌佢 最多都係事後幫佢洗返乾淨咁 都算<br />\n<br />\n但今日呢件事我真係嬲到屌咗佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n噉佢就有個公事包 平時帶返工嘅 平時喺街到會放底喺地下 但返到屋企又周圍亂放 搞到屋企污糟晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日我一返到屋企 竟然俾我見到佢放咗個公事包喺我張床到 我即刻嬲到癡線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大叫咗句 : 屌你老母!!<br />\n<br />\n我立即除鞋 將佢個公事包喺我張床到拎走再開佢拖 佢仲好意思話我洗咩噉大反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問下大家 應該點再教育佢好 或者點整走條撚屌好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02479e008bc2fb65bedd2ff1fdee8b1dd3b0aabe","tid":938864,"uid":183194,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T15:58:30.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母，使唔使咁大反應啊"},{"pid":"111cf16c49317a5ea8351f8f5534b33582f52ee0","tid":938864,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02479e008bc2fb65bedd2ff1fdee8b1dd3b0aabe","tid":938864,"uid":183194,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T15:58:30.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母，使唔使咁大反應啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T15:59:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42bb849204bd74973aefa8441371c45069a9e8df","tid":938864,"uid":42246,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T16:00:15.000Z","msg":"潔癖唔係病來既咩？<br />\n依家自己有潔癖重屌鳩人咁撚惡既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f443f0bf9fc3d32d0e3c93c94640135a7720bbaf","tid":938864,"uid":123304,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T16:01:49.000Z","msg":"我覺得做人基本衛生一定要有，好憎人未沖涼就著污糟衫上床"},{"pid":"ce24e87c89fae37043fa57e36878a8e2e279262d","tid":938864,"uid":199590,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"f443f0bf9fc3d32d0e3c93c94640135a7720bbaf","tid":938864,"uid":123304,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T16:01:49.000Z","msg":"我覺得做人基本衛生一定要有，好憎人未沖涼就著污糟衫上床"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T16:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一出過街 個人就已經污糟咗 絕對唔可以上床<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75038d9f3f61f706658160f219ef16173a18d372","tid":938864,"uid":209663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T16:05:43.000Z","msg":"我唔覺得係潔癖！係基本衛生！"},{"pid":"19f92fc407a16ee96926a5638d937934bd6e2db9","tid":938864,"uid":209663,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ce24e87c89fae37043fa57e36878a8e2e279262d","tid":938864,"uid":199590,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"f443f0bf9fc3d32d0e3c93c94640135a7720bbaf","tid":938864,"uid":123304,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T16:01:49.000Z","msg":"我覺得做人基本衛生一定要有，好憎人未沖涼就著污糟衫上床"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T16:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一出過街 個人就已經污糟咗 絕對唔可以上床<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T16:08:17.000Z","msg":"絕對正確 冇得駁咀"},{"pid":"0c8c664b60b59b8f51f70f15f15515bf83026fa0","tid":938864,"uid":152298,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20